  Steadfast:

    Whenever this Pokémon flinches, 
  its Speed rises one stage.

  Inner-focus:

    This Pokémon cannot flinch.

  Justified:

    Whenever a dark-type move hits 
  this Pokémon, its Attack rises 
  one stage.

